                        <i class="fas fa-book-open"></i> Our Story
                    </button>
                    <button class="tab-link" onclick="openAboutTab(event, 'mission')">
                        <i class="fas fa-bullseye"></i> Our Mission
                    </button>
                    <button class="tab-link" onclick="openAboutTab(event, 'special')">
                        <i class="fas fa-star"></i> Why Choose Us
                    </button>
                </div>

                <div id="story" class="tab-content active">
                    <h3>Our Story</h3>
                    <p>We started with a simple idea: make reading accessible to everyone, everywhere. Our digital library brings thousands of books right to your fingertips, creating a space where knowledge meets convenience.</p>
                </div>

                <div id="mission" class="tab-content">
                    <h3>Our Mission</h3>
                    <p>We believe that reading should be accessible, affordable, and enjoyable for all. Our mission is to break down barriers between people and knowledge, offering both purchase and borrowing options to suit everyone's needs.</p>
                </div>

                <div id="special" class="tab-content">
                    <h3>Why Choose Us</h3>
                    <p>Unlike traditional bookstores, we offer the flexibility to both buy and borrow. Our curated collection ensures quality content, while our user-friendly platform makes finding your next great read effortless.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

